{"title":"Trek Project One Chills Out with Crystalline Arctic Haze","link":"https://bikerumor.com/trek-project-one-chills-out-with-crystalline-arctic-haze/","date":1700863412000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-3.jpg\" alt=\"trek project one crystalline arctic haze paint on a road bike\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-3.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-3-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>The latest custom paint option from Trek’s Project One is called Crystalline Arctic Haze, and it’s a beaut. Inspired by (or a nod to) those who rise before dawn to train and ride through any weather, good or bad.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The fade may look simple…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of trek project one crystalline arctic haze paint\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-4-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>…as if getting a perfectly blended fade between two colors is simple (it’s not)…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of trek project one crystalline arctic haze paint\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-2-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>…but this one runs through a spectrum of morning sky hues.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of trek project one crystalline arctic haze paint\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-1-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The lower third stays dark, but gets its own unique lattice structure formed by using thousands of crystals, hence the name.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of trek project one crystalline arctic haze paint\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/trek-project-one-icon-crystalline-arctic-haze-5-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s available now on all of Trek’s premium road bikes through their dealers and online.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.trekbikes.com\" target=\"_blank\">TrekBikes.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/trek-project-one-chills-out-with-crystalline-arctic-haze/\">Trek Project One Chills Out with Crystalline Arctic Haze</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"6b4f3d3bd7cfe8f79deab9cd35b54e648eb300ddc729d6c2ad16a92a968ee9e6","category":"Cycling"}